sed secure content sniffing for web browsers supporting text and image files; a pairing free certificateless group key agreement protocol with constant round; enhancing the security levels in WLAN via novel IBSPS; varying password based scheme for user authentication; DCT based robust multi-bit steganographic algorithm; service adaptive broking mechanism using MROSP algorithm; performance comparison of hypervisors in the private cloud; an ant colony based load balancing strategy in cloud computing; a demand based resource provisioner for cloud infrastructure; large scale cloud for biometric identification; implementation of symmetric functions using quantum dot cellular automata; dynamic page replacement at the cache memory for the video on demand server; hybrid function based analysis of simple networks; performance augmentation of a FAT filesystem by a hybrid storage system; an approach for compiler optimization to exploit instruction level parallelism; architecting fabricated implant in interconnect for multi-core processor; data concentration on torus embedded hypercube network; SAT based scheduling in high level synthesis; hybrid function based microprocessor realisation of closed loop analysis and synthesis; RFID for indoor position determination; to reduce training cost in EW simulations; detection of communities in social networks using spanning tree; implementation of compressed brute-force pattern search algorithm using VHDL and a modified collaborative filtering approach for collaborating community.
