AB  - The proceedings contain 115 papers. The special focus in this conference is on International Conference on Industrial Design and Mechanical Power. The topics include: The analysis of a simplified 2R pseudo-rigid-body model with moment load; explore the design of communication products for the aging population; a quality attribute for RFID manufacturing system; optimizing the performance of chip shooter machine based on ant colony algorithm; experimental study of gravity heat pipe with ECT; design of hydraulic system for soft roll calender; structural failure analysis of shaft of wobbly and attrited testing equipment; analysis of cutting zone machinability during the drilling of XCr18Ni8 stainless steel; research on immersive virtual assembly technology; study on key technology in making rice by high-altitude pressure cooker; research and design of customer analysis system based on clustering minin; study on key technologies of the green furniture design; structural optimization of suspension mechanism based on APDL; simulation analysis of motor vehicle ride comfort based on Adams; strength analysis and safety design of baby car seat; load distribution of cross-roller slewing bearing; stochastic response surface method with enhanced weighting strategy; analysis of the mechanical properties of slewing bearings using finite element method; the application of ANSYS Stress concentration analysis technique to etch pit analysis on inhaul cable; a characteristic brake system model for passenger car; design of 3D modeling for the new hammer mill based on the solidworks; effect of sunroofs and side windows on aerodynamic characteristics of transit bus; electroless Ni-La-P coatings on 2024 aluminum alloys for aircraft structure; the study of three-layer quantum dots system; parameter mapping method for multi-system design of automotive chassis; finite element analysis on energy dissipation ability of geo-materials under impact load; exploration on aerodynamic noise characteristics for control valve of steam turbine; short-term wind power forecasting based on SVM with backstepping wind speed of power curve; dynamic analysis of a ducted fan UAV in forward flight; three dimensional gis monitoring system of mineral pipeline transporting system.
