tion of the response surface; the stochastic EM algorithm for censored mixed models; existence of higher order convergent quasi-Monte Carlo rules via Walsh figure of merit; ANOVA decomposition of convex piecewise linear functions; hit-and-run for numerical integration; QMC galerkin discretization of parametric operator equations; on the choice of weights in a function space for quasi-Monte Carlo methods for a class of generalised response models in statistics and multi-level Monte Carlo finite difference and finite volume methods for stochastic linear hyperbolic systems.
